description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 20, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 60, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 3 for East, 1 for South, and 8 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10203-93180-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [60 Votes, Common]
